videos.description: Michigan's Moritz Wagner tries finishing in the paint but is rejected by Maryland's Michal Cekovsky.
videos.headline: Cekovsky rejects Wagner

videos.description: Maryland's Michal Cekovsky finds an opening down the middle and finishes the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Cekovsky throws down two-handed slam

videos.description: Maryland's Anthony Cowan draws contact from Michigan's Zavier Simpson and finishes the tough layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Cowan converts tough layup for 3-point play

videos.description: Maryland's Anthony Cowan pulls up from behind the arc and sinks the difficult 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Cowan drills tough 3-point shot

videos.description: Michigan's Charles Matthews lofts a pass up to Jon Teske for the alley-oop layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Matthews finds Teske on the oop

videos.description: Michigan's Muhammad-Ali Abdur-Rahkman swings the ball out to Duncan Robinson for the wide open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Abdur-Rahkman finds Robinson for open 3

videos.description: With the shot clock running down, Anthony Cowan pulls up from behind the arc and sinks the long 3-point shot.
videos.headline: Cowan shows off range on long 3-pointer

videos.description: Michigan's Charles Matthews feeds Moritz Wagner cutting to the basket for the layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Matthews sets up Wagner's lay-in

videos.description: Michigan's Zavier Simpson swings the ball out to Moritz Wagner for the 3-pointer, cutting Maryland's lead to 3.
videos.headline: Wagner's 3 cuts into Maryland's lead

videos.description: Michigan's Zavier Simpson splits through the defense and converts the tough floater for a 3-point opportunity.
videos.headline: Simpson sinks difficult floater for and-1 chance

videos.description: Michigan's Jordan Poole drives down the lane and converts the crafty reverse layup to extend Michigan's lead to 5.
videos.headline: Poole converts reverse lay-in

videos.description: Michigan's Jordan Poole leads Jon Teske down the paint for the contested layup and chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Teske finishes tough layup for and-1 opportunity

videos.description: Maryland's Anthony Cowan drives to the paint and nails the tough reverse lay-in.
videos.headline: Cowan sinks athletic reverse layup

videos.description: Maryland's Darryl Morsell finds Kevin Huerter in the corner for a contested 3-pointer late in the second half.
videos.headline: Huerter sinks corner 3-ball

videos.description: Michigan's Zavier Simpson drives down the paint and converts the finger roll late in the second half.
videos.headline: Simpson converts lay-in to extend Michigan's lead

videos.description: Maryland's Michal Cekovsky dishes the ball out to Kevin Huerter for the big 3-pointer, giving Maryland a 1-point lead.
videos.headline: Huerter converts clutch 3-pointer
